 The Who 可以进行头像秀吗？罗杰·达尔特雷回应https://www.nme.com/news/music/could-the-who-ever-do-an-avatar-show-roger-daltrey-responds-3761360?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=could-the-who-曾经做过阿凡达秀罗杰达尔特雷回应Tom SkinnerFri, 31 May 2024 16:36:48 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3761360 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Who-Roger-Daltrey-posing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="谁人乐队 (The Who) 的罗杰·达尔特雷 (Roger Daltrey) 在舞台上现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Who-Roger-Daltrey-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Who-Roger-Daltrey-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Who-Roger-Daltrey-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Who-Roger-Daltrey-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Who-Roger-Daltrey-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Who-Roger-Daltrey-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他还开玩笑说乐队可以“出去翻唱 ABBA”</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/could-the-who-ever-do-an-avatar-show-roger-daltrey-responds-3761360">The Who 可以进行头像秀吗？ Roger Daltrey 的回应</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Who-Roger-Daltrey-posing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="谁人乐队 (The Who) 的罗杰·达尔特雷 (Roger Daltrey) 在舞台上现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Who-Roger-Daltrey-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Who-Roger-Daltrey-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Who-Roger-Daltrey-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Who-Roger-Daltrey-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Who-Roger-Daltrey-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/The-Who-Roger-Daltrey-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/roger-daltrey">罗杰·达尔特雷 (Roger Daltrey)</a>谈到了未来<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-who">The Who</a>进行阿凡达巡演或演出的可能性。</p><p>今年早些时候，主唱的乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pete-townshend">皮特·汤森德</a>在接受<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2024/03/23/theater/pete-townshend-tommy-broadway.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《纽约时报》</em></a>采访时简要提到了这个想法。这位吉他手告诉媒体， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pete-townshend-says-the-who-have-one-final-thing-left-to-do-before-they-crawl-off-to-die-3609212">他希望乐队在“爬行去死”之前“演奏世界上的每一个地区”</a> 。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/roger-daltrey-on-teenage-cancer-trust-and-the-chances-of-new-music-from-the-who-3410696">罗杰·达尔特雷 (Roger Daltrey) 谈论青少年癌症信托基金以及 The Who 推出新音乐的机会</a></strong></li></ul><p>但汤森德后来解释说，“谁不是达尔特雷和汤森德在80岁的时候在舞台上假装年轻”。 “这是 1964 年我们四个人的故事，当时我们 18 岁或 19 岁，”他补充道。 “如果你想看谁人神话，就等着看阿凡达秀吧。这将是很好的！”</p><p>现在，达尔特雷在接受<a href="https://ultimateclassicrock.com/roger-daltrey-who-avatar-tour/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Ultimate Classic Rock</em></a>采访时被问及是否同意 Townhend 对 The Who 数字表演的看法。</p><p>该出版物引用了本月在伦敦举行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/abba-voyage-live-in-london-review-photos-video-setlist-2-3235227">ABBA Voyage</a>盛典，庆祝了其两周年纪念日，以此作为这种形式的例子。</p><p>对此，达尔特雷开玩笑说：“什么，我们要出去翻唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/abba">ABBA</a> ？我不这么认为。我穿迷你裙会看起来很糟糕！” </p><figure id="attachment_3448731" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3448731" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3448731" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ABBA_Voyage_Stage.jpg" alt="阿巴航程" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ABBA_Voyage_Stage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ABBA_Voyage_Stage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ABBA_Voyage_Stage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ABBA_Voyage_Stage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ABBA_Voyage_Stage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ABBA_Voyage_Stage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3448731" class="wp-caption-text"> ABBA Voyage 在伦敦 ABBA Arena 举行。图片来源：ABBA Voyage</figcaption></figure><p>在停下来考虑虚拟 Who 演出的前景后，这位歌手补充道：“我从来没有想过这个问题。我不想去看。”</p><p>达尔特雷将于下个月开始<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-whos-roger-daltrey-announces-solo-north-american-tour-3603143">北美“半原声”独奏巡演</a>。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.com/roger-daltrey-tickets/artist/1335441?irgwc=1&amp;clickid=QHQVEUQchxyPR5sWCQS0k2gbUkHX02VvcSNiXA0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;impradid=2862475&amp;REFERRAL_ID=tmfeedbuyat2862475&amp;wt.mc_id=aff_BUYAT_2862475&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;impradname=NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;ircid=4272" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里查找剩余的门票</a>。</p><p>本月早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-would-be-bang-up-for-oasis-hologram-show-after-watching-abbas-voyage-concert-3756769">诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher) 表示，在观看 ABBA Voyage 音乐会后，他将“为 Oasis 的全息表演而兴奋不已”</a> 。 “说实话，我对此印象深刻，”他解释道。</p><p>去年12月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-first-kiss-avatar-shows-will-take-place-in-2027-3562981">KISS确认他们的首轮阿凡达表演将于2027年举行</a>。</p><p>乐队于 12 月 2 日在麦迪逊广场花园进行了最后一场现实生活演出，为他们的“End Of The Road”世界巡演画上了圆满的句号。在那里，他们宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kiss-announce-new-era-as-a-virtual-band-3552477">未来将继续以虚拟化身的身份，</a>据报道成为第一个这样做的美国团体。</p><p>作为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-the-chemical-brothers-and-young-fathers-to-play-2024-teenage-cancer-trust-gigs-3566977">今年青少年癌症信托基金会演出系列</a>的一部分<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-who-kick-off-teenage-cancer-trust-2024-with-huge-orchestral-show-3603467">，谁人乐队三月份在伦敦皇家阿尔伯特音乐厅演奏了两场管弦乐演出</a>。第二天晚上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eddie-vedder-joined-the-who-on-stage-at-royal-albert-hall-last-night-for-tct-3607351">，埃迪·维德 (Eddie Vedder) 意外客串</a>亮相。</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/could-the-who-ever-do-an-avatar-show-roger-daltrey-responds-3761360">The Who 可以进行头像秀吗？ Roger Daltrey 的回应</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
