/www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Pearl-Jam-Eddie-V-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Pearl-Jam-Eddie-V-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>昨晚（5 月 30 日） <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pearl-jam">Pearl Jam</a>在西雅图翻唱了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nine-inch-nails">Nine Inch Nails</a>的《Hurt》——观看下面的表演。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="141" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/pearl-jam-dark-matter-album-review-lyrics-tracklist-3618556"><b>Pearl Jam – “暗物质”评论：他们近期记忆中最出色的一些作品</b></a></li></ul><p>在乐队在西雅图气候承诺竞技场举行的家乡演出中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eddie-vedder">埃迪·维德</a>在 18,000 名歌迷面前演奏了这首歌，以标志着他们“暗物质”巡演北美站的结束。</p><p>在演出的其他地方，Pearl Jam 还首次在巡演中现场演唱了两首曲目：“Pilate”和“Love Boat Captain”。该乐队还翻唱了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/neil-young">Neil Young</a>的《Rockin&#39; In The Free World》。</p><p>您可以查看下面封面的粉丝镜头以及完整的歌单。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">没想到这个人来了。 <a href="https://twitter.com/eddievedder?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@eddievedder</a>今晚在 @climatepledgearena 现场翻唱<a href="https://twitter.com/nineinchnails?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@nineinchnails</a>的“Hurt”！ 5/30/24 <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/pearljam?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#pearljam</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/nineinchnails?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#nineinchnails</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/hurt?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#hurt</a> <a h